data.description: The charming Ranch style house boasts 2 BRs, 1 BA, & a one car detached garage with easy access from the garage to kitchen making carrying in groceries a breeze. The fenced-in backyard is perfect for families with kids & pets, offering them a secure & safe space to play & unwind. Although unfinished, the basement presents an opportunity for buyers to personalize it to their liking & style. The front porch welcomes a perfect place to sip on that morning coffee or enjoy time with friends, family and neighbors. Located close to Blank Park Zoo, residents can take a leisurely walk to see the beautiful animals or take their kids to explore the playgrounds. The house's location also offers easy access to Hwy 5 and easy drive to downtown. Additionally, it is incredibly close to Des Moines International Airport.
